      <hedline>
        <hl1>Optimum Takes On Media Planning</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Elliott, Stuart</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Optimum Media, media buying and research division of DDB Needham Worldwide, is assuming media planning functions of sibling, Griffin Bacal, making Optimum a full-service media services agency; Steven Naftelberg, media director at Griffin Bacal, takes that position at Optimum Media Planning (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Optimum Media, the media buying and research division of the DDB Needham Worldwide unit of Omnicom Group, is assuming the media planning functions of a sibling, Griffin Bacal, making Optimum a full-service media services agency.</p>
        <p>Steven Naftelberg, 39, media director at Griffin Bacal, takes that position at Optimum Media Planning, reporting to Page Thompson, president of Optimum Media.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Optimum Media, the media buying and research division of the DDB Needham Worldwide unit of Omnicom Group, is assuming the media planning functions of a sibling, Griffin Bacal, making Optimum a full-service media services agency.</p>
        <p>Steven Naftelberg, 39, media director at Griffin Bacal, takes that position at Optimum Media Planning, reporting to Page Thompson, president of Optimum Media.</p>
        <p>Griffin Bacal's media buying had already been handled by Optimum Media.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
